'''Francis Philip McGlone''' (born November 1948) is a [[neuroscientist]] at [[Liverpool John Moores University]], where he is the head of the [[Somatosensory system|Somatosensory]] & [[Affective neuroscience|Affective Neuroscience]] Group.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ljmu.ac.uk/about-us/staff-profiles/faculty-of-science/natural-sciences-and-psychology/francis-mcglone|title=Francis McGlone|website=Ljmu.ac.uk|accessdate=27 November 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.liverpool.ac.uk/neuroscience-group/people/francis-mcglone/|title=Professor Francis McGlone Professor Francis McGlone- Liverpool Neuroscience Group - University of Liverpool|website=Liverpool.ac.uk|accessdate=27 November 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.liverpool.ac.uk/pain-research-institute/our-people/francis-mcglone/|title=Francis McGlone - Pain Research Institute - University of Liverpool|website=Liverpool.ac.uk|accessdate=27 November 2017}}</ref>

==Selected publications==
