==Autonomous statistical services at sub-national level== Some countries are politically organised as federations of states or of autonomous regions; also a specific territory might have been given a partial autonomy. Several of these sub-national regional units have set their own quasi-independent statistical department. A list is presented in [[Sub-national autonomous statistical services]]
